JW3   *   GET LINE# FROM SORT NAME
 |    *================================================================
 |   C**         #GETL     BEGSR
 |    *
 |   C**                   MOVE *BLANK    LIN#    2
 |   C**                   MOVE 'N'       OKFLG   1
 |   C**                   MOVEAO@SRT     T7A
 |   C**                   MOVEA*BLANK    T7B
 |   C**                   Z-ADD0         IY      10
 |   C**         1         DO   7         IX      10
 |   C**         T7A,IX    IFGE '0'
 |   C**         T7A,IX    ANDLE'9'
 |   C**                   ADD  1         IY
 |   C**                   MOVE T7A,IX    T7B,IY
 |   C**                   ENDIF
 |   C**                   ENDDO
 |    *
 |   C**         IY        IFNE 0
 |   C**         T7B,2     IFEQ *BLANK
 |   C**                   MOVE T7B,1     T7B,2
 |   C**                   MOVE 0         T7B,1
 |   C**                   ENDIF
 |   C**                   MOVE 'Y'       OKFLG
 |   C**                   MOVEAT7B       LIN#
 |   C**                   ENDIF
 |    *
JW3  C**                   ENDSR
